    <item>
      <title>舒尔茨将于 10 月 12 日接待拜登、斯塔默和马克龙参加乌克兰会谈</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/scholz-to-host-biden-starmer-macron-for-ukraine-talks-oct-12</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据德国政府高级官员透露，德国总理奥拉夫·朔尔茨将于周六在柏林接待美国、法国和英国领导人，就乌克兰问题举行会谈。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/scholz-to-host-biden-starmer-macron-for-ukraine-talks-oct-12</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 10:32:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国对欧盟汽车和白兰地征收反倾销税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/china-slaps-levy-on-european-brandy-amid-worsening-trade-ties</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国正在调查是否提高对欧洲大引擎汽车的关税，并将开始对白兰地征收税款，这在欧盟决定对中国电动汽车征收关税后，加剧了贸易争端。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/china-slaps-levy-on-european-brandy-amid-worsening-trade-ties</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 07:07:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列将在美国举行会谈，因伊朗反击而紧张局势加剧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/israel-defense-chief-to-head-to-us-as-iran-retaliation-looms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列国防部长将前往华盛顿，该国正在考虑如何应对一周前伊朗的导弹袭击，并加强对黎巴嫩真主党的军事行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/israel-defense-chief-to-head-to-us-as-iran-retaliation-looms</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 06:04:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫迪领导的政党有望在印度邦选举中意外获胜</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/modi-s-support-tested-as-two-indian-provinces-begin-vote-counts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪领导的政党有望在哈里亚纳邦立法机构选举中取得意外胜利，这将提升该党在未来几个月关键的地区选举中的前景。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/modi-s-support-tested-as-two-indian-provinces-begin-vote-counts</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 02:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里斯称她稍后将考虑乌克兰加入北约</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/harris-says-she-ll-weigh-ukraine-nato-membership-at-later-point</link>
      <description><![CDATA[民主党总统候选人卡玛拉·哈里斯拒绝透露当选后是否会支持乌克兰加入北约，但她发誓，她将坚持让基辅领导人参与美国与弗拉基米尔·普京就结束持续冲突进行的任何谈判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/harris-says-she-ll-weigh-ukraine-nato-membership-at-later-point</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 01:06:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
